ity to meet constraints, system stability, and changes\noccurring in power system parameters, such as, mechanical power input and\ninertia.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Sep 2019 00:00:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 15:54:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-19"}
