QT in an important new application area: epilepsy diagnosis\nin sub-Saharan Africa where only low-field scanners are normally available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Sep 2019 08:56:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-17"}
